---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Review Terkirim - LITBOKS">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="mb-8">
        <svg class="mx-auto h-16 w-16 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Review Terkirim!</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
        Terima kasih telah berbagi review Anda. Review akan ditampilkan setelah melalui moderasi.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-4">Apa Selanjutnya?</h2>
        <ul class="text-left space-y-3 text-blue-800">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="mr-2">1.</span>
            <span>Review Anda akan dimoderasi dalam 24 jam ke depan</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="mr-2">2.</span>
            <span>Setelah disetujui, review akan ditampilkan di halaman buku</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="mr-2">3.</span>
            <span>Anda dapat menulis review untuk buku lainnya</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="space-x-4">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700">
          Kembali ke Beranda
        </a>
        <button 
          onclick="history.back()" 
          class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-gray-300 text-base font-medium rounded-md text-gray-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50"
        >
          Kembali ke Buku
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout> 